long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The legacy version of Fulcro Inspect extension. Since version 3 the Fulcro Inspect extension only works with recent versions of Fulcro. This is an old version that will remain working for users that are in Fulcro 2.
